_639_1":"zh","vote_average":2.278},{"width":1175,"height":1763,"file_path":"/asxPR6oTEBj6uM88ep876kaQ1pj.jpg","iso_639_1":"en","vote_average":2.066},{"width":530,"height":750,"file_path":"/gdNhcy94K1fa3OPrSUZlWrTMQ6G.jpg","iso_639_1":"zh","vote_average":1.75},{"width":1400,"height":2100,"file_path":"/ghZw8AY4AgypSr5BmZcTAsX8bXN.jpg","iso_639_1":"de","vote_average":1.75}],"backdrops":[{"width":3840,"height":2160,"file_path":"/1McO40rFBnUSz0EB2EwYQlUv9LV.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":2.278},{"width":1920,"height":1080,"file_path":"/dSwLzM4NxJp0aLsBJWcbZLtF7Oc.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":1.75},{"width":1920,"height":1080,"file_path":"/klioTuA8JepFgV0EC7IxqV6VbrM.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":1.75},{"width":3840,"height":2160,"file_path":"/xm8h3tkzYL3cCy4o3luNEe0WVyE.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":1.75},{"width":3000,"height":1688,"file_path":"/hrGnBXv9FAXXR3aAie69xsxOHTo.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":1.222},{"width":1920,"height":1080,"file_path":"/bDBAVnB6JkBfQzAd7B7sz5RhChQ.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":1.222},{"width":3000,"height":1688,"file_path":"/sNHtqdtGmfkktvXevzxqcbldr7N.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":1.066},{"width":3000,"height":1688,"file_path":"/jufbNQHeDM2jXt3CPXuKR6ofpXl.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":0.958},{"width":3000,"height":1688,"file_path":"/fEPHU7pmySZrTCOuiQP9dJbtfDi.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":0.958},{"width":3000,"height":1688,"file_path":"/uEFZRhYjpKPS4J1u0ajL8nbjzBV.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":0.958},{"width":3000,"height":1688,"file_path":"/5ZYWNM2BDqK41xjr6nj9rGMS5vk.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":0.958},{"width":2268,"height":1275,"file_path":"/1TZBypbCOPRIddeUp8z2qCa2ke0.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":0.166},{"width":3000,"height":1688,"file_path":"/98B5OKssif8KhP9YE5SnjP0EfCd.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":0.166},{"width":3000,"height":1688,"file_path":"/tfP74z3aNHVWHdRJNy0L76fqhhx.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":0.166},{"width":3000,"height":1688,"file_path":"/zIW0TshjQGSpjziDN0bWRW9kOBO.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":0.166}]},"enriched_at":"2026-04-21T07:27:51.134+00:00","enrichment_cycle":1,"translations":[{"data":{"title":"哭悲","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"新型病毒蔓延，全世界的人們對病毒逐漸麻木，沒人相信病毒的突變和濳藏危機即將到來。俊喆和他的女友凱婷討論疫情何時結束，但生活還是一如往常。某天早上，俊喆騎車送凱婷去上班分開後，兩人分別目睹不明暴徒的襲擊事件：包括早餐店老闆被阿婆撲倒狂咬、隔壁鄰居拿著武器大街狂奔、各地的暴動事件頻傳，恐慌、尖叫聲在全城蔓延。遭感染的異常人類遍布，被虐殺的血腥畫面滿街都是，大狂殺恐怖襲來，誰能活下來？俊喆要如何殺出活路，拯救不知去向的心愛女友？"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"TW","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"The Sadness","runtime":100,"tagline":"It feels...wonderful...","homepage":"","overview":"A young couple is pushed to the limits of sanity as they attempt to be reunited amid the chaos of a pandemic outbreak. The streets erupt into violence and depravity, as those infected are driven to enact the most cruel and ghastly things imaginable."},"name":"English","iso_639_1":"en","iso_3166_1":"US","english_name":"English"},{"data":{"title":"The Sadness","runtime":0,"tagline":"Sembra... Meraviglioso...","homepage":"","overview":"Una giovane coppia cerca di ritrovarsi in una città devastata da un'epidemia. Le cose peggiorano quando il virus subisce una mutazione dando il via a nuovi orrori.\r Mentre esplode una pandemia internazionale, una coppia cerca di ritrovarsi per mettersi quanto più al sicuro. Ma non sarà affatto semplice.\r Le strade, infatti, sono popolate impunemente dai contagiati che, anziché isolarsi, si stanno lasciando andare a una folle spirale di violenza e depravazione, commettendo atti di estrema crudeltà contro tantissimi malcapitati.\r Torture e uccisioni rappresentano il quadro scabroso che si sta drammaticamente osservando: appare tutto come il tramonto della civiltà conosciuta. Per i due protagonisti di questa storia, giungere alla salvezza sarà un’impresa quanto mai proibitiva…"},"name":"Italiano","iso_639_1":"it","iso_3166_1":"IT","english_name":"Italian"},{"data":{"title":"哭悲","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"《哭悲》故事描述新型病毒蔓延，全世界的人们对病毒逐渐麻木，没人相信病毒的突变和濳藏危机即将到来。往常。某天早上，俊喆骑车送凯婷去上班分开后，两人分别目睹不明暴徒的袭击事件：包括早餐店老板被阿婆扑倒狂咬，隔壁邻居拿着武器大街狂奔，各地的暴动被感染的异常人类发出的“嘎嘎嘎呕”的声音，遍布街头，被虐杀的血腥画面满街都是，大狂杀恐怖袭击来，谁能活下来？俊喆要如何杀出活路，拯救不知去向的心爱女友？"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"CN","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"The Sadness","runtime":0,"tagline":"Der wohl brutalste Zombiefilm aller Zeiten!","homepage":"","overview":"In Taiwan breitet sich eine aggressive Mutation des neuartigen Alvin-Virus aus, doch das Land ist gespalten, wie es mit der Pandemie umgehen soll. Während die Regierung den Ernst der Lage herunterspielt, müssen die Menschen auf den Straßen um ihr Leben kämpfen. Die Straßen werden mehr und mehr bevölkert von sadistischen, sexuell enthemmten Monstern, die die Stadt in ein regelrechtes Blutbad verwandeln. Mord, Folter, Vergewaltigung und andere Gewaltexzesse nehmen eine verstörende Eigendynamik an. Inmitten des grausamen Gemetzels setzt der junge Junzhe (Tzu-Chiang Wang) alles daran, seine Freundin Kai Ting (Regina Lei) zu finden, die er am Morgen noch am anderen Ende Taipehs zu ihrer Arbeit gebracht hat. Auf der Suche nacheinander müssen sie bis zum Äußersten gehen, um eine Chance auf das Überleben zu haben."},"name":"Deutsch","iso_639_1":"de","iso_3166_1":"DE","english_name":"German"},{"data":{"title":"The Sadness","runtime":100,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Après un an de lutte contre une pandémie aux symptômes bénins, une nation finit par baisser sa garde. C'est alors que le virus mute spontanément, donnant naissance à un fléau qui altère l'esprit. Les rues se déchaînent dans la violence et la dépravation, les personnes infectées étant poussées à commettre les actes les plus cruels et les plus horribles qu'elles n'auraient jamais pu imaginer..."},"name":"Français","iso_639_1":"fr","iso_3166_1":"FR","english_name":"French"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"العربية","iso_639_1":"ar","iso_3166_1":"SA","english_name":"Arabic"},{"data":{"title":"The Sadness","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Una pareja joven es llevada al límite de la cordura mientras trata de reunirse en medio del caos de un brote pandémico. Las calles se convierten en violencia y depravación, a medida que los infectados se ven empujados a realizar las cosas más crueles y horribles que te puedas imaginar. Asesinato, tortura, violación y mutilación son solo el comienzo. Ya pasó la era de la civilidad y el orden. Solo queda 'The Sadness'."},"name":"Español","iso_639_1":"es","iso_3166_1":"ES","english_name":"Spanish"},{"data":{"title":"Последний день на Земле","runtime":99,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Уже год на Земле бушует эпидемия загадочного вируса, к которой большинство населения планеты относится несерьезно. Молодая пара, как и многие, продолжает жить обычной жизнью, и однажды по пути на работу они сталкиваются с агрессивными плотоядными согражданами. Вирус мутировал неожиданным образом."},"name":"Pусский","iso_639_1":"ru","iso_3166_1":"RU","english_name":"Russian"},{"data":{"title":"The Sadness","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Město Tchaj-pej náhle propuká v krvavý chaos, a to kvůli viru, díky kterému jsou lidé nuceni vraždit, mučit a dělat spoustu horších ohavností. Mladý pár je dohnán až na hranici zdravého rozumu, když se snaží znovu sejít uprostřed této strašné apokalypsy. Doba pořádku a radosti je pryč, zůstává pouze a jen „smutek“"},"name":"Český","iso_639_1":"cs","iso_3166_1":"CZ","english_name":"Czech"},{"data":{"title":"哭悲","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"台灣被病毒籠罩，人人被感染後變得暴力，殺戮處處。情侶俊喆及凱婷正想辦法逃過一劫. . ."},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"HK","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"곡비","runtime":0,"tagline":"가장 잔혹한 지옥이 찾아온다!","homepage":"","overview":"평범한 사람들이 상상할 수 있는 가장 끔찍하고 잔인한 것들을 강박적으로 행동하게 바뀌면서, 타이베이시는 갑자기 피비린내 나는 아수라장이 된다. 살인, 고문, 절단은 단지 시작일 뿐이다. 한 젊은 커플은 이 폭력과 타락의 도가니 속에서 서로 만나기 위해 노력하고 거의 정신줄을 놓을 지경에 다다른다. 질서와 예의의 시대는 끝났다. 이 도시엔 오직 슬픔만이 남았을 뿐."},"name":"한국어/조선말","iso_639_1":"ko","iso_3166_1":"KR","english_name":"Korean"},{"data":{"title":"Szomorúság","runtime":99,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"A világjárvány elleni küzdelem után végre fellélegezhet az emberiség. Ám a vírus spontán mutálódik, és egy tudatmódosító járványt hoz létre. Az utcákon kitör az erőszak és a romlottság, a fertőzöttek a legkegyetlenebb és legszörnyűbb dolgokat követik el. A gyilkosság, a kínzás, a nemi erőszak és csonkítás csak a kezdet. A civilizáltság és a rend kora lejárt. Csak a \"Szomorúság\" létezik."},"name":"Magyar","iso_639_1":"hu","iso_3166_1":"HU","english_name":"Hungarian"},{"data":{"title":"Đại Dịch Thần Chết","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Một cặp đôi trẻ cố gắng tìm nhau trong một thành phố bị tàn phá bởi một loại bệnh dịch kỳ lạ - nạn nhân của dịch này trở thành những kẻ tàn bạo điên cuồng, khát máu."},"name":"Tiếng Việt","iso_639_1":"vi","iso_3166_1":"VN","english_name":"Vietnamese"},{"data":{"title":"A Tristeza","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Um jovem casal tenta se reencontrar no meio de uma cidade devastada por uma praga que transforma suas vítimas em sádicos insanos e sanguinários."},"name":"Português","iso_639_1":"pt","iso_3166_1":"BR","english_name":"Portuguese"},{"data":{"title":"哭悲/THE SADNESS","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://klockworx-v.com/sadness/","overview":"台北を拠点に活躍する、カナダ出身のロブ・ジャバス監督によるエクストリーム・ホラー。人間の凶暴性を助長する謎の感染症が蔓延し、殺人と拷問であふれかえる台湾を舞台に、生きて再会しようとする男女の姿を描く。"},"name":"日本語","iso_639_1":"ja","iso_3166_1":"JP","english_name":"Japanese"},{"data":{"title":"העצבות","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"זוג צעיר מנסה להתאחד בתוך עיר שהושחתה במגפה שהופכת את קורבנותיה לסאדיסטים מטורללים וצמאי דם."},"name":"עִבְרִית","iso_639_1":"he","iso_3166_1":"IL","english_name":"Hebrew"},{"data":{"title":"The Sadness","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Ett muterat virus gör smittade invånare i Taipei till bindgalna, blodtörstiga varelser som mördar helt utan hämningar och misskund. Fast på motsatta sidor av staden när det groteska blodbadet tar sin början försöker det unga paret Kat och Jim att hitta varandra i det fruktansvärda kaoset. Men hur ska de klara det när vardagens gator blivit ett helvete på jorden och en mentalt förvrängd pöbel som lever ut sina sjukaste fantasier på alla de får tag i står mellan dem och återförening?"},"name":"svenska","iso_639_1":"sv","iso_3166_1":"SE","english_name":"Swedish"},{"data":{"title":"Smutek","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Zmutowany wirus atakuje mózgi i zamienia zainfekowanych w opętanych żądzą mordu, seksu i gwałtu zwyrodnialców."},"name":"Polski","iso_639_1":"pl","iso_3166_1":"PL","english_name":"Polish"},{"data":{"title":"The Sadness","runtime":100,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Nuoret rakastavaiset Jim ja Kat heräävät uuteen aamuun aurinkoisessa miljoonakaupungissa. Uutisissa puhutaan irti päässeestä viruksesta, mutta se ei tunnu kiinnostavan ketään. Kun Jim on heittänyt Katin skootterillaan töihin, arki suistuu raiteiltaan. Eri puolilta kaupunkia kantautuu tietoja järkensä menettäneistä ihmisistä ja selittämättömistä veriteoista. Tapahtumien syystä ei ole tietoa, mutta tilannekuva on selvä: pakoon. Mahdollisimman nopeasti ja kauas, mitään keinoja kaihtamatta."},"name":"suomi","iso_639_1":"fi","iso_3166_1":"FI","english_name":"Finnish"},{"data":{"title":"La Tristeza","runtime":0,"tagline":"Se siente...maravilloso...","homepage":"","overview":"Una joven pareja intenta reunirse en medio de una ciudad devastada por una plaga que convierte a sus víctimas en sádicos enloquecidos y sedientos de sangre."},"name":"Español","iso_639_1":"es","iso_3166_1":"MX","english_name":"Spanish"},{"data":{"title":"غم و اندوه","runtime":0,"tagline":"حسش... فوق‌العاده است...","homepage":"","overview":"یک زوج جوان در حالی که تلاش می‌کنند در میان هرج و مرج ناشی از شیوع یک بیماری همه‌گیر، دوباره به هم بپیوندند، به مرزهای سلامت عقل سوق داده می‌شوند. خیابان‌ها به خشونت و تباهی کشیده شده است، زیرا افراد آلوده به اعمال ظالمانه‌ترین و وحشتناک‌ترین چیزهایی که قابل تصور است واداشته شده‌اند."},"name":"فارسی","iso_639_1":"fa","iso_3166_1":"IR","english_name":"Persian"},{"data":{"title":"Cмуток","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"Український","iso_639_1":"uk","iso_3166_1":"UA","english_name":"Ukrainian"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"SG","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"Türkçe","iso_639_1":"tr","iso_3166_1":"TR","english_name":"Turkish"}],"reviews_tmdb":[{"id":"69472a5151f19264968eb39e","url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/review/69472a5151f19264968eb39e","author":"patient1","content":"This is setting up to be Horrorific, as we've got the cutest couple opening our story with the start of their day. And it begins in the most Gruesome manner, and you won't believe your eyes at the Sheer Brutality of the scenes. \r\n  This is one to remember as It's very much like open warfare on the senses with lots of generous amounts of Pure Terror and Oodles of Gore, and where Bravery will be met with Unbridled and Wanton Ferocity. \r\n  It's Impressive how much Compassion people have when all is in Pure Kaos, and people are in Full Depravity Mode.","created_at":"2025-12-20T22:59:29.329Z","updated_at":"2025-12-20T22:59:29.339Z","author_details":{"name":"","rating":8,"username":"patient1","avatar_path":null}}],"recommendations":[{"id":40108,"adult":false,"title":"Emmanuelle: Queen of Sados","video":false,"overview":"A woman struggles to keep her stepdaughter from harms way after she hires an assassin to kill her husband, but the hitman turns and blackmails her for the crime.","genre_ids":[80,18,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":2.1974,"vote_count":119,"poster_path":"/rKK9i0ewgN4S1KbX7pc3BOWUWO8.jpg","release_date":"1980-02-01","vote_average":6.172,"backdrop_path":"/smjGg5K8e6zofjSSc5o5xOnflLI.jpg","original_title":"Η Μαύρη Εμμανουέλα","original_language":"el"},{"id":367085,"adult":false,"title":"Sad?","video":false,"overview":"Set in the mid sixties and shot with more black than white, ‘SAD?’ is a dark ten minute film that explores the time that we spend alone watching television, and the good and sad effects it can have on you. The film has a timeless, forgotten feel about it, a study of a world and time detached from the norm, a life filled with both laughter and loneliness, escapism and escapees...","genre_ids":[99],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.0331,"vote_count":34,"poster_path":null,"release_date":"1996-01-18","vote_average":5.9,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"Sad?","original_language":"en"},{"id":547205,"adult":false,"title":"SeX","video":false,"overview":"","genre_ids":[878],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.7018,"vote_count":33,"poster_path":"/SanxKtBGtiiYLSEMqOg8wWTtxT.jpg","release_date":"2003-12-04","vote_average":6.182,"backdrop_path":"/12993jceLZtiVAtDKL57SRch5bI.jpg","original_title":"SeX","original_language":"es"},{"id":583132,"adult":false,"title":"Sadako","video":false,"overview":"A psychologist connects her missing brother to the strange case of a mysterious little girl believed to be Sadako reincarnated.","genre_ids":[27],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.2625,"vote_count":122,"poster_path":"/wCanUYBbUxADpfqpoe3tmQ3KVL6.jpg","release_date":"2019-05-24","vote_average":5.889,"backdrop_path":"/v7wKtlycdR35iB7f5VmKc1mmUYx.jpg","original_title":"貞子","original_language":"ja"},{"id":760919,"adult":false,"title":"The Power","video":false,"overview":"London, 1974. As Britain prepares for electrical blackouts to sweep across the country, trainee nurse Val arrives for her first day at the crumbling East London Royal Infirmary. With most of the patients and staff evacuated to another hospital, Val is forced to work the night shift, finding herself in a dark, near empty building. Within these walls lies a deadly secret, forcing Val to face both her own traumatic past and deepest fears.","genre_ids":[27],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.7785,"vote_count":168,"poster_path":"/s0aVEjT1DWopUrJehACWZyqpO99.jpg","release_date":"2021-06-03","vote_average":6.024,"backdrop_path":"/lQ7OF8zoLMOh1rxL0iwWXr28jk0.jpg","original_title":"The Power","original_language":"en"},{"id":602301,"adult":false,"title":"Josée","video":false,"overview":"Young-seok, who feels overwhelmed and lonely in what should be his glorious youth, meets a woman who introduces herself as Josée, and they share a once-in-a-lifetime romance.","genre_ids":[10749,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.1027,"vote_count":61,"poster_path":"/8SmPto6JQ1zTANDffKPi2yUW1YJ.jpg","release_date":"2020-12-10","vote_average":7.148,"backdrop_path":"/tXUmghBMpKE2NvpNtMCYzofIazQ.jpg","original_title":"조제","original_language":"ko"},{"id":508466,"adult":false,"title":"Sad Hill Unearthed","video":false,"overview":"Province of Burgos, northern Spain, October 2015. A group of fans undertake the titanic task of restoring the location of the last scene of The Good, the Bad and the Ugly, the mythical spaghetti western directed by Italian filmmaker Sergio Leone in 1966.","genre_ids":[99,36],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.3321,"vote_count":112,"poster_path":"/1DgoWzjWlLzN4GuLgrIe2iScTPt.jpg","release_date":"2018-10-19","vote_average":6.942,"backdrop_path":"/jJMayZ9Pz66DEU7AocbiU4HuejC.jpg","original_title":"Sad Hill Unearthed","original_language":"es"},{"id":1094403,"adult":false,"title":"Malum","video":false,"overview":"A rookie police officer willingly takes the last shift at a newly decommissioned police station in an attempt to uncover the mysterious connection between her father's death and a vicious cult.","genre_ids":[27],"media_type":"movie","popularity":3.8814,"vote_count":155,"poster_path":"/m1rcLLs0KmS8Cg60sLoMZC2OyDR.jpg","release_date":"2023-03-31"